lead_paragraph: The majorities for Cottman (Independent Whig) in the Sixth Congressional District, are as follows: (Somerset, 767; Worcester, 75. For Henry Talbot, regular Whig,) 267. Dorchester to hear from. Cottman is elected. By the Southern mail which arrived to-night, we learn that late frosts have greatly injured the crops in Georgia.
